/* XIAO nRF54LM20B: the board already provides the USB CDC UART
 * (cdc_acm_uart) as the chosen console, so no app-level console override is
 * needed. This overlay is intentionally a no-op on 20B. (The previous override
 * to a self-defined cdc_acm_uart0 node left that node without a backing device
 * struct, which broke DEVICE_DT_GET(DT_CHOSEN(zephyr_console)).)
 */
